t against Germany changed the course of the war.  a4310aUnited States.bArmy Air Forces.bBomb Group, 303rd. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xAerial operations, American. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xCampaignszWestern Front. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xRegimental historieszUnited States.  aD 790.253 303rd S76 2015hUAHS-Bi0162035248408  aD 790.253 303rd S76 2015wLCc1i0162035248408lON_SHELFmUAHSSp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu3/4/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n96112597bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/9119392